{"tid":1187043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳： 反送中貼紙乍現各區 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-06-05T10:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T10:55:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b66b37e232b6bdf9a796631a4d51848916aee381","tid":1187043,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:55:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190604/20694895\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190604%2F20694895&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=95d46376\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190604%2F20694895&h=797acdc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190604/20694895</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n反送中貼紙乍現各區 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190604/large/a1703a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190604%2Flarge%2Fa1703a.gif&h=c8be86f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反送中貼紙出現喺香港不同角落。吳文遠fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂通過後，人人都有被移交危機，如果𠵱家唔發聲，唔知第時仲有冇機會反抗？但八方對港人好有信心，睇見近日聯署反應，證明好多香港人熱愛呢個仲有自由嘅城市。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：隔牆有耳：你參唔參加？ 運動平台吹雞 6.9齊怒跑<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇留意到，呢幾日喺不同角落有唔少反送中貼紙，提醒港人唔好忘記歷史？社民連主席吳文遠喺facebook貼圖，從佢po嘅相可見，港鐵站內地圖及出口指示以及街上嘅燈柱等，都貼上呼籲6.9上街反送中嘅貼紙，以及前特首梁振英1989年譴責中共屠城嘅報紙廣告等，今日六四30年，真係特別令人感觸。 <br />\n<br />\n而喺中西區各處，亦乍現大量反送中貼紙，甚至貼喺建制派區議員橫額。有西環居民報料，指由堅尼地城到半山區都見到呢款貼紙，一如聯署，6.9上街嘅訊息，已經遍地開花。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190604/large/a1703b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190604%2Flarge%2Fa1703b.gif&h=46318112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190604/large/a1703c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190604%2Flarge%2Fa1703c.gif&h=8a9b818c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：你參唔參加？ 運動平台吹雞 6.9齊怒跑 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：你參唔參加？ 運動平台吹雞 6.9齊怒跑"}]}